# Firebase Admin SDK service account keys and RTDB export dumps — these
# contain real credentials / real student data and must NEVER be committed.
# Named explicitly (not a blanket *.json) so package.json, tsconfig*.json,
# firebase.json, firestore.indexes.json etc. stay tracked as normal.
serviceAccountKey.json
service-account*.json
rtdb-export*.json
*.firebase-adminsdk-*.json
